data.description: Escape the city for the serene country life on 1.31 acres. Just minutes from shopping and restaurants. Roomy 2800+ sq ft home with 2 car garage PLUS a fantastic RV/boat garage. Gourmet kitchen, living room, dining room, main bedroom on main level. Stained, white oak hardwood floors. The RV garage is 44 x 14, wide and should accommodate slide outs. New gas water heater and furnace. Workshop has loft. Flat, grassy yard and a large chicken coop. Deer fenced large garden. Extra storage shelf in garage. 2nd RV spot w/hookups. Come view today!
